snippet.title: The Empty Desk - PC Game Demo Trailer Reveal
snippet.description:
The Empty Desk is a psychological thriller adventure with puzzles and horror elements. Detective Bennett of the London Homicide Unit must uncover dark secrets while navigating a reality-bending environment that tests his sanity.

Play the FREE demo on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3421770/The_Empty_Desk_Demo/

Enjoy!
